snippet.textDisplay:
I think this is a story arc and we are watching 2 factions, not 1 group. It looks like you have a group of 3 performing rituals in the woods (plain black cloaks, faces never shown.) Behind, them a skull faced "watcher," possibly hunter, wearing the only cloak with the white cross pursues them. The last scene shows one of the "coven" arms raised, which I think is from the hunter's perspective as he approaches drawing dagger from behind.

So, I am voting "not a cult." :D Welcome back, guys.
